OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few heavy showers across the
OL,6,Fsouthwest of Cornwall. Otherwise a
OL,7,Fmostly dry albeit cloudy day with a
OL,8,Ffew showers around, these mainly in
OL,9,Fthe west. Best of the sunshine
OL,10,Fconfined to the east of the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing overnight,
OL,13,Fleaving the region dry with patchy
OL,14,Fcloud and some clear spells. Most
OL,15,Fplaces staying above freezing with the
OL,16,Frisk of some grass frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
