OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry start to the day with
OL,6,Fvariable cloud. Showers developing
OL,7,Finto the afternoon which can be slow
OL,8,Fmoving and heavy. Dry in the south and
OL,9,Fwarmer than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fmixed weekend with showers in places,
OL,13,Fbut bright or sunny spells not far
OL,14,Faway. More showers in the southwest on
OL,15,FMonday but temperatures will drop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
